{"tid":577530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子一出門就摔死　KTV安全出口竟懸空10米","createTime":"2018-03-01T23:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T10:31:53.000Z","uid":81228,"like":143,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"3c291d3235e786354c0a22a166f3c9c36746397a","tid":577530,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"網路上有時會看到「懸空門」的詭異設計，往往只是讓人覺得好笑，想不到中國一名女子真的因此喪命。河南一名27歲女子郭夏，趁著春節返鄉與國中同學相約到駐馬店市一間KTV唱歌聚會，席間因為要接電話，便想從安全出口出去比較安靜，豈料這個安全出口竟然懸空10公尺高，郭夏一跨出就墜落5樓斃命。<br />\n<br />\n據《都市頻道》報導，2月11日晚上，郭夏和國中同學到駐馬店市正陽縣紫星城KTV聚會，過程中郭夏接到電話，因為包廂裡太吵，郭夏便到走廊，看到一個門上面標註「安全出口」，便想走出去講電話，結果這個門竟然是一個懸空門，她一出門就墜樓，單側肋骨全斷，當場喪命。郭夏的妹妹哽咽痛批：「推開門下面就是懸崖，你看像懸崖不？當場掉下去就沒有命了。」<br />\n<br />\n原來該門KTV根本是無照營業，去年兩度被縣府下令要求改善，但業者仍然繼續營業。事後KTV吳姓負責人因涉嫌過失致人死亡罪被警方拘留，至於死者賠償問題，則仍在進行協商。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180301/640_7a7fb1ca44dc7ec380ba01ebc08c9943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180301%2F640_7a7fb1ca44dc7ec380ba01ebc08c9943.jpg&h=0f396ce6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKTV懸空門。翻攝自《都市頻道》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180301/640_aec6d6eaa786a5a2b50cf39e8c6b851d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180301%2F640_aec6d6eaa786a5a2b50cf39e8c6b851d.jpg&h=79c89e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者妹妹表示，安全出門推開卻宛如懸崖。翻攝自《都市頻道》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180301/640_49057e43b69f3597832747d574123a93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180301%2F640_49057e43b69f3597832747d574123a93.jpg&h=1fef0c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死者郭夏。翻攝自《都市頻道》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180301/1306310/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180301%2F1306310%2F&d=m8so%2FOR4F3kCltcsHZh%2B5NU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3341a4b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180301%2F1306310%2F&h=9f9e6bbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180301/1306310/</a>"},{"pid":"414acbdbe68a7f5acfa0a8f7b1d923209687849d","tid":577530,"uid":52215,"like":1011,"dislike":5,"score":1006,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/075216_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F075216_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=ef46b44c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58f21f8abe3ca688e5d90e0f6ee7862eaa7cfbba","tid":577530,"uid":30169,"like":239,"dislike":2,"score":237,"quote":{"pid":"414acbdbe68a7f5acfa0a8f7b1d923209687849d","tid":577530,"uid":52215,"like":1011,"dislike":5,"score":1006,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/075216_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F075216_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=ef46b44c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"係支那真係可以成真"},{"pid":"7e9725f4d2460ebb75bb9c08b390d74f8ee8b6ba","tid":577530,"uid":10757,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:53:52.000Z","msg":"安全出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e0d885ae010f1745a888453545d538092f5ae8","tid":577530,"uid":40226,"like":120,"dislike":1,"score":119,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T23:54:58.000Z","msg":"連鎖都唔鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d725b833e9cad1dc61d5199